'From Squeak3.7alpha of 11 September 2003 [latest update: #5707] on 20 February 2004 at 11:28:37 pm'!"Change Set:		TextStyleNameDate:			21 February 2004Author:			sdadd knowStyle without default information"!!TextStyle class methodsFor: 'TextConstants access' stamp: 'sd 2/20/2004 23:08'!knownTextStylesWithoutDefault	"Answer the names of the known text styles, sorted in alphabetical order without default"	"TextStyle knownTextStylesWithoutDefault"	| result |	result := self knownTextStyles asOrderedCollection.	result remove: #DefaultFixedTextStyle.	result remove:  #DefaultTextStyle.	^ result! !